		<title>TikTok重獲新生 ! 中美達成協議 將繼續在美運營</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/17/tiktok%e9%87%8d%e7%8d%b2%e6%96%b0%e7%94%9f-%e4%b8%ad%e7%be%8e%e9%81%94%e6%88%90%e5%8d%94%e8%ad%b0-%e5%b0%87%e7%b9%bc%e7%ba%8c%e5%9c%a8%e7%be%8e%e9%81%8b%e7%87%9f/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 00:03:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
